en_809153_0	The new Shrine Room at Mahawelithenna Primary School was constructed by 2 (V) Sri Lanka Signal Corps (SLSC) troops on the instructions of the 2 (V) SLSC Commanding Officer, Lieutenant Colonel Bathiya Jayaweera.
en_809153_1	Financial support for the construction was made available by Mr Duminda Jayaweera and Mr Ranga Warusavithana at the invitation of Lieutenant Colonel Bathiya Jayaweera.
en_809153_2	The shrine room was formally handed over to the children in the primary school during a simple ceremony attended by Maha Sangha, Officers and Other Ranks of 2 (V) SLSC, parents and students.
